
URL = http://www.fairpensions.org.uk


=Description=

"FairPensions campaigns for major institutional investors to adopt responsible
investment, using shareholder power to hold companies to account. In addition
to letting people know about the power of their pension to improve corporate
behaviour, it runs single issue campaigns to bring shareholder pressure on
companies. For example, in 2010 FairPensions co-ordinated a coalition of
institutional and individual investors and successfully filed resolutions on the oil
sands in Canada to the AGMs of Royal Dutch Shell plc. and BP."


